## Steps for MVP

1. logic for starting game
- PRESS THE START BOTTOM AND APPEAR A TABLE WITH THE 9 SPACES ON THE CENTER 
2. Moves
 - WHEN YOU CLICK ON A SQUARE THE "X" APPEARS, THEN THE PLAYER 2 CHOOSES WHERE TO PUT THE "O" AND SO;

3.  logic for losing and//or winning
THE PLAYER WHO MAKES  A VERTICAL/HORIZONTAL OR DIAGONAL ROW WITH THE THREE NOUGHTS OR CROSSES AFTER 5 CHOOSES IS THE WINNER AND THE GAME IS OVER,
IN CASE OF TIE APPEARS, THE GAME MUST BE RESTARTED;

